        <div class="res-card"><div class="res-title" style="color:#fbbf24">Bureau sent back "Verified"</div><div class="res-body">Send a Method of Verification letter (FCRA §611(a)(7)). Then escalate to a CFPB complaint at consumerfinance.gov/complaint. Finally, dispute directly with the original creditor's disputes department.</div></div>
