        <div class="res-card"><div class="res-title" style="color:#c084fc">Round 1 (Days 1–30)</div><div class="res-body">Pull reports, run Credit AI analysis. Send FDCPA §809 debt validation to all collectors via certified mail. Send FCRA §611 dispute letters to all 3 bureaus for every questionable item. Pay down utilization to under 10%.</div></div>
