            <div>
              <div style="font-family:'Cabinet Grotesk',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:16px;color:#60a5fa">Convenience Checks &#8212; The Complete Guide</div>
              <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted)">Paper checks from your card issuer that deposit directly into your bank &#8212; the cleanest way to turn credit into cash at low cost</div>
