        <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;margin-bottom:16px">The complete self-repair system from scratch. Every step, every letter, every law.</p>
        <div class="disclaimer-box">
          <strong>&#9888;&#65039; DISCLAIMER:</strong> This content is provided for <strong>educational purposes only</strong>. Clear Pro Consultant LLC is not a law firm and does not provide legal advice. Nothing here constitutes legal advice or creates an attorney-client relationship. Individual credit situations vary significantly. <strong>Results are not guaranteed.</strong> For complex legal situations, consult a licensed consumer law attorney. Information reflects current law as understood at time of publication — laws and bureau policies may change.
