          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:14px">
            <div style="font-size:26px">&#9875;&#65039;</div>
            <div>
              <div style="font-family:'Cabinet Grotesk',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:17px;color:#60a5fa">How to Get Into Navy Federal Credit Union</div>
              <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px">The most valuable credit union in the country &#8212; here is how to qualify</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:12px 16px;border-radius:10px;background:rgba(96,165,250,.08);border:1px solid rgba(96,165,250,.2);font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:14px">
            Navy Federal has some of the best cards in the country &#8212; low APRs, no foreign transaction fees, high limits, and genuine member service. Membership is restricted to the military community, but the eligibility rules are broader than most people realize. There are legitimate paths in for almost anyone with a qualifying connection, even an indirect one.
